reviewText: If you are familiar with the show, then you know what you are getting yourself into with this buy.  I have always been a big fan of the Pee Wee movies and shows.  I wish that he would have been wiser in his personal life and I'd feel less creepy having my kids watch these shows.  Regardless, my kids love this boxset.  I love watching these shows with them too.  This is a good price for a lot of Pee Wee entertainment.  Santa brought this one to us for Christmas.  The included Christmas special is also very neat to watch, he had a lot of Hollywood stars on that show, it was amazing to see how many people wanted to be a part of Pee Wee's Christmas special.
summary: A whole lot of Pee Wee.

reviewText: What a trip back to Saturday mornings in the 80s.  For a while, I used to watch this almost every Saturday.  I remember watching it with my brother, and sometimes with my cousins who would have sleepovers at my house, and we'd always have a good laugh.  We'd laugh at the show and say it was silly.  That classic theme song sung by Cyndi Lauper and the show openings were great.  I even remember seeing an advertisement for a new show coming to tv, Perfect Strangers, that was to become another favorite show of mine, during a commercial break while watching this show.Watching it now as an adult, I can see how odd, crazy and great the show was.  It's still very funny.  My family watched the dvds together and we all got a good laugh.  Sometimes, I focus on the show and it's ability to make me laugh now.  Other times, I really get into the nostalgia as the show totally takes me right back to childhood.  That feeling of sitting on the sofa, or a sleeping bag on the floor, in the living room, watching our old tv set, and eating a bowl of cereal.
Title: N/A

reviewText: This is a "bundle" package of the previously releasedPee-wee's Playhouse #1 - Seasons 1 and 2,Pee-wee's Playhouse #2 - Seasons 3-5andPee Wee's Playhouse Christmas Special. They were wonderful for kids and adults when they ran on the air back in late 80's. Pure Saturday Morning Magic! Those who bought the DVD sets just mentioned should be assured that none of these products have any differing special features or additional commentaries as compared to their original DVD releases-- these ARE the original DVD releases sold in a bundle so that the purchaser can buy them all in one fell (and reasonably priced) swoop. Bargain hunters will want to purchase the individual products used and save some coin.
summary: Excellent material, but not a new or expanded edition
